Extending the Tool
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
• Authenticating with APIs:  
  - Store your API keys or tokens (e.g., OpenAI key, Zapier webhook URLs, Google credentials, Shopify private app key) in environment variables or a secure config file (e.g., .env).  
