  - Establish an OAuth or Service Account flow.

• Automation with Zapier:  
  - Fire events or webhooks to Zapier from Node.js, or set up a Zap that pulls data from your system.  
  - Possibly create separate commands for each Zap-based workflow.

• Managing Shopify Products:  
  - Use Shopify’s Admin API endpoints (REST or GraphQL).  
  - Insert code to list, update, or create products within the challenges or list-systems commands as needed.

• Using ChatGPT for text generation:  
  - Use the official OpenAI Node.js library or direct HTTP calls with fetch.  
  - Provide an option or subcommand to generate text or summarize data on the command line.

